{"tid":2356151,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"(有圖) 日本嫌犯移除《生死格鬥》角色服裝後製成 DVD 販售遭移送法辦","createTime":"2021-01-06T15:13:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T03:30:10.000Z","uid":54930,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"dc7932dcda1f83ccab8b51a940d1dea818893181","tid":2356151,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T15:13:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=208897\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgnn.gamer.com.tw%2Fdetail.php%3Fsn%3D208897&d=tgCcTb3Ji4LFIEkqsM1g5oeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=8da2c0aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=208897</a><br />\n日本嫌犯移除《生死格鬥：沙灘排球維納斯假期》角色服裝後製成 DVD 販售遭移送法辦<br />\n（GNN 記者 RU 報導） 2021-01-06 15:18:53<br />\n  光榮特庫摩今日發表官方公告，日本一名嫌犯疑似擅自錄製該公司旗下知名作品《生死格鬥：沙灘排球維納斯假期》等遊戲內動畫，並將角色衣服加以刪除、修改內容後製作成 DVD 進行販售，已遭神奈川縣警方將相關資料送往檢方偵辦，而此案除了刑事案件外，也計畫提起民事訴訟。<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/B/2KU/60/d22b6bbdee557b77f438c719b31b0eo5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FB%2F2KU%2F60%2Fd22b6bbdee557b77f438c719b31b0eo5.JPG&h=dd7c9fd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/B/2KU/69/dece107adfb29a001849e46ba71b03t5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FB%2F2KU%2F69%2Fdece107adfb29a001849e46ba71b03t5.JPG&h=82e09bfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  公告中指出，該名嫌犯錄製了《生死格鬥：沙灘排球維納斯假期》作品內的動畫，並刪除角色身上衣服等遭修改的內容製作成 DVD，放到拍賣網站上進行販售。光榮特庫摩向神奈川縣警方報案，而嫌犯刪除服裝等擅自變更內容部分也認為是有侵害著作權（複製權）的行為。<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/B/2KU/17/a59bb6be5f98e386f31e6127d61b3x95.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FB%2F2KU%2F17%2Fa59bb6be5f98e386f31e6127d61b3x95.JPG&h=bb286179&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  公告指出，此案被認定是惡質行為，因此除了刑事案件部分外，他們也將基於侵害著作權的損害賠償問題來提起民事訴訟。光榮特庫摩指出，未經該公司許可，將旗下作品加以複製（包括部分內容改編）並加以散佈販售是侵害著作權人的行為，是違法的，他們將會嚴格看待此種行為。<br />\n<a href=\"https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=208897\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgnn.gamer.com.tw%2Fdetail.php%3Fsn%3D208897&d=tgCcTb3Ji4LFIEkqsM1g5oeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=8da2c0aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=208897</a>"},{"pid":"d3590fea19097d22c9a169b9f1e3b816e8ac24cb","tid":2356151,"uid":63311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T15:14:21.000Z","msg":"腦魔最愛"},{"pid":"efaf37c146a26358e0c8cb6c9a6a2efc41538043","tid":2356151,"uid":286155,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T15:15:28.000Z","msg":"光榮自己唔出又唔俾人整真係賤格"},{"pid":"b6f79ef935b5ff26c8ba4602fc06a8ffa538a26c","tid":2356151,"uid":9,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T15:16:30.000Z","msg":"本身佢自己都出到好意淫"},{"pid":"4c06b100ab945f65f37edd804628233d0b20919c","tid":2356151,"uid":310700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T15:19:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />gay"},{"pid":"07986e4326988f13fc669cfe52fd478dffc737de","tid":2356151,"uid":91931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T15:21:20.000Z","msg":"自己開隻hs2抽插飽佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"303e0a3b4febd1f5e6f07405237970a9e2bcb1f0","tid":2356151,"uid":76216,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T15:56:58.000Z","msg":"上網大把mod免費<br />\n係都要拎黎賣 抵啦"},{"pid":"b8048cced6424027b4fbe2f190ad088c9f1e5fa5","tid":2356151,"uid":61954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07986e4326988f13fc669cfe52fd478dffc737de","tid":2356151,"uid":91931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T15:21:20.000Z","msg":"自己開隻hs2抽插飽佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime